{"id":330272,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/【微历史】：五毛们否认大饥荒/","date":"2014-01-22T23:35:09Z","modified":"2014-01-22T21:25:22Z","title":"【微历史】：五毛们否认大饥荒","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi5.jpg\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi5.jpg\" alt=\"weilishi5\" width=\"606\" height=\"491\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330273\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi5.jpg 606w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi5-300x243.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px\" /></a></p>\n<p>浩正刘臻：晚上吃饭听同学谈他外公的遭遇，唏嘘不已：本是几代地方望族，土改顷刻一无所有，转眼赶上大饥荒，为挣口饭吃去河边拉纤，口粮都留给孩子，最后自己活活饿死了！最后说起五毛们否认大饥荒，叫嚣：你们谁家真饿死过人时，他眼含热泪，目露凶光……</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.botanwang.com/articles/201401/〖微历史〗邓榕刘亭亭参与对卞仲耘的行凶.html\">图片来自网络</a></p>\n","author":296,"categories":[18270,18269,17016,10466],"tags":[23277,9997,24532]}